    Metallic\",\n    \"m_Content\": \"We will use another Branch to set the Metallic
    property of the Fragment shader. This will be identical to the Branch we used
    to set the Alpha, but when the predicate evaluates to False, we want the Metallic
    property to be 0 rather than 0.8.\",\n    \"m_TextSize\": 0,\n    \"m_Theme\":
    0,\n    \"m_Position\": {\n        \"serializedVersion\": \"2\",\n        \"x\":
