    \"m_Title\": \"1. Hex Pattern\",\n    \"m_Content\": \"Create a Hex Lattice node:
    this will instantiate the subgraph we just implemented. Set the input parameters
    to \\nTiling: (10, 10)\\nHex Scale: 1\\nEdge Width: 0.2\",\n    \"m_TextSize\":
    0,\n    \"m_Theme\": 0,\n    \"m_Position\": {\n        \"serializedVersion\":
    \"2\",\n        \"x\": -1070.0,\n        \"y\": 758.6666870117188,\n        \"width\":
